channel.title: Mopar's stuck at "Loading - Please wait"!
channel.description: Well, this happens occasionallyL I go on a server and I log in, but then while everything is loading, like my inventory (usually you get money on stuff upon logging in a new account for some server) and the welcome messages in the chat box loads, but the screen is stuck on "Loading - Please wait" and it's all black. How do i fix this???

item.title: Mopar's stuck at "Loading - Please wait"!
